'''2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭'''（{{lang-hy|Հայ-ադրբեջանական_պատերազմ 2020}}；{{lang-az|2020 Qarabağ döyüşləri}}），又稱為'''第二次納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭'''、'''第二次納卡戰爭'''或'''-{zh-tw:兩亞戰爭;zh-hans:阿亚战争;zh-hant:阿亞戰爭;}-'''，是[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫]]地区在[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]、[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]和[[阿尔察赫共和國|阿尔察赫]]之間的一场[[武裝衝突|武裝衝突]]，始于2020年9月27日的早晨，沿着纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫边界地区[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫接触线|接触线]]展開。为应对此次衝突，[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]和[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]宣布[[戒严|戒严]]并且全国[[总动员|总动员]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://in.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan-martial-law/nagorno-karabakh-announces-martial-law-and-total-mobilization-idINKBN26I086?il=0|title=Nagorno-Karabakh announces martial law and total mobilization|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2020-09-27|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002075716/https://in.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan-martial-law/nagorno-karabakh-announces-martial-law-and-total-mobilization-idINKBN26I086?il=0%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]宣布戒严和[[宵禁|宵禁]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan-curfew/azerbaijans-parliament-approves-martial-law-curfews-presidents-aide-idINKBN26I0OU|title=Azerbaijan's parliament approves martial law, curfews – president's aide|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2020-09-27|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927194535/https://www.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan-curfew/azerbaijans-parliament-approves-martial-law-curfews-presidents-aide-idINKBN26I0OU/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於9月28日宣佈部份動員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apa.az/en/azerbaijan-army-azerbaijani-armed-forces/Partial-mobilization-announced-in-Azerbaijan-331385|title=Partial mobilization announced in Azerbaijan|publisher=Azeri Press Agency（阿塞拜疆通讯社）|date=2020-09-28|accessdate=2020-09-28|archive-date=2020-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012130547/https://apa.az/en/azerbaijan-army-azerbaijani-armed-forces/Partial-mobilization-announced-in-Azerbaijan-331385|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於11月10日，雙方簽署停火協議，亞塞拜然勝利。

許多國家和[[聯合國|聯合國]]強烈譴責衝突，並呼籲雙方緩和緊張局勢，毫不拖延地恢復有意義的談判<ref name="f24_300920">{{Cite web|date=2020-09-30|title=UN Security Council calls for immediate end to fighting in Nagorno-Karabakh|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200930-un-security-council-calls-for-immediate-end-to-fighting-in-nagorno-karabakh|access-date=2020-09-30|agency=Associated Press|website=France 24|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009133111/https://www.france24.com/en/20200930-un-security-council-calls-for-immediate-end-to-fighting-in-nagorno-karabakh|dead-url=no}}</ref>。土耳其向阿塞拜疆提供了軍事支持，儘管其支持程度存在爭議<ref name="russiamatters01" /><ref name=voa28sep>{{cite news |last1=Jones |first1=Dorian |title=Turkey Vows Support for Azerbaijan in Escalating Nagorno-Karabakh Conflict |url=https://www.voanews.com/south-central-asia/turkey-vows-support-azerbaijan-escalating-nagorno-karabakh-conflict |work=[[美国之音|美国之音]] |date=2020-09-28 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200930203704/https://www.voanews.com/south-central-asia/turkey-vows-support-azerbaijan-escalating-nagorno-karabakh-conflict |archivedate=2020-09-30 |quote=“Turkey is already supporting Azerbaijan militarily, through technical assistance through arms sales, providing critical military support, especially in terms of armed drones and technical expertise', said Turkish analyst Ilhan Uzgel.” |accessdate=2020-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

國際分析家認為，戰鬥可能是由[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]發起的<ref name="russiamatters01">{{cite web |last1=Kofman |first1=Michael |title=Armenia–Azerbaijan War: Military Dimensions of the Conflict |url=https://www.russiamatters.org/analysis/armenia-azerbaijan-war-military-dimensions-conflict |website=Russia Matters |publisher=Belfer Center for Science and International Affairs |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201003115234/https://www.russiamatters.org/analysis/armenia-azerbaijan-war-military-dimensions-conflict |archivedate=2020-10-03 |date=2020-10-02 |quote=Turkey has publicly, and militarily, backed Azerbaijan in this conflict. |accessdate=2020-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="eurasianet_290920">{{Cite web|last1=Kucera|first1=Joshua|date=2020-09-29|title=As fighting rages, what is Azerbaijan's goal?|url=https://eurasianet.org/as-fighting-rages-what-is-azerbaijans-goal|accessdate=2020-09-29|website=EurasiaNet|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004115811/https://eurasianet.org/as-fighting-rages-what-is-azerbaijans-goal|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其進攻的主要目標很可能是佔領納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫南部的山區，因為該地區没有那麼多山和相對於防禦工事更多的內部山區更容易佔領<ref name="fp_280920">{{cite news|last=Palmer|first=James|date=2020-09-28|title=Why Are Armenia and Azerbaijan Heading to War?|work=[[Foreign_Policy|Foreign Policy]]|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/09/28/why-are-armenia-azerbaijan-heading-to-war-nagorno-karabakh/|access-date=2020-09-29|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928222614/https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/09/28/why-are-armenia-azerbaijan-heading-to-war-nagorno-karabakh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。土耳其對阿塞拜疆的支持被認為是試圖通過擴大阿塞拜疆在衝突中的地位以及將俄羅斯在該地區的影響力邊緣化來擴大其勢力範圍<ref name="russiamatters01"/>。

於2020年10月10日，經[[俄罗斯|俄羅斯]]調解後，在[[红十字国际委员会|红十字国际委员会]]的協助下，由亞美尼亞和阿塞拜疆雙方同意了一個脆弱的人道主義停火<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|date=2020-10-11|title=Armenia Azerbaijan: Reports of fresh shelling dent ceasefire hopes|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-54488386|access-date=2020-10-11|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010002202/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-54488386|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月17日，亞美尼亞和阿塞拜疆雙方外交部发表联合声明，再次同意自18日凌晨零时起「人道停火」。但第2次人道停火协议生效不到4分钟，亚美尼亚指控[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]在凌晨零时4分发动炮火攻击<ref name=":1" />。10月26日，亞美尼亞和阿塞拜疆在美國居中協調下第3次宣布停火协议，不過在隔日生效后迅速宣告失败，两国互控对方违反由美国居中斡旋的停火协议<ref>{{Cite web|title=亚美尼亚亚塞拜然第3次人道停火 刚生效就破功|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E4%BA%9A%E5%A1%9E%E6%8B%9C%E7%84%B6%E7%AC%AC3%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-%E5%88%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88%E5%B0%B1%E7%A0%B4%E5%8A%9F/46122402|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=zh|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120155618/https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E4%BA%9A%E5%A1%9E%E6%8B%9C%E7%84%B6%E7%AC%AC3%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB-%E5%88%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88%E5%B0%B1%E7%A0%B4%E5%8A%9F/46122402|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月9日，在俄羅斯居中協調下，亞美尼亞和阿塞拜疆第4次宣布停火协议<ref>{{Cite web|title=俄总统：亚美尼亚亚塞拜然同意全面停火|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%BF%84%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F-%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E4%BA%9A%E5%A1%9E%E6%8B%9C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB/46151944|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=zh|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120155622/https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%BF%84%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F-%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E4%BA%9A%E5%A1%9E%E6%8B%9C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB/46151944|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
{{further|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫冲突|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争}}
纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫地區以亞美尼亞人為主要民族，目前由[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]支持的[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]实际控制，但国际上普遍承认为[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]的领土。為爭奪這一地區，雙方於1988年2月至1994年5月之間曾爆发过[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]。在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]斡旋下，雙方在1994年簽訂了{{le|比什凱克停火協議|Bishkek Protocol}}，雙方於實控線停火由亞美尼亞人控制阿尔察赫及周邊地區。在2007年，兩國曾在西班牙[[馬德里|馬德里]]就[[歐洲安全與合作組織|歐洲安全與合作組織]]明斯克小组提出的{{le|馬德里方案| Madrid Principles}}進行和平谈判，惟亞美尼亞在2020年3月明確拒絕了此一方案<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-09-18|title='Velvet Populism' Ends Decade-Long Discussion Of The Madrid Principles - OpEd|url=http://www.eurasiareview.com/18092020-velvet-populism-ends-decade-long-discussion-of-the-madrid-principles-oped/|access-date=2020-09-30|website=Eurasia Review|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108120708/https://www.eurasiareview.com/18092020-velvet-populism-ends-decade-long-discussion-of-the-madrid-principles-oped/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在比什凱克停火協議至2020年9月的武裝衝突之間，兩國曾經發生過多次武裝衝突，當中最嚴重的是[[2016年亞美尼亞–亞塞拜然衝突|2016年衝突]]和[[2020年7月亞美尼亞－阿塞拜疆武裝衝突|2020年7月衝突]]，各造成雙位數字的傷亡<ref>{{Cite web|last=Ministère de l'Europe et des Affaires étrangères|title=Armenia/Azerbaijan – Border clashes between the two countries (15 Jul. 2020)|url=https://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files/armenia/news/article/armenia-azerbaijan-border-clashes-between-the-two-countries-15-jul-2020|access-date=2020-09-27|website=France Diplomacy – Ministry for Europe and Foreign Affairs|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002075938/https://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/country-files/armenia/news/article/armenia-azerbaijan-border-clashes-between-the-two-countries-15-jul-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

