key-Azerbaijan military drills intimidate Armenia, President Aliyev says | work =Daily Sabah | date =2020-09-20 | accessdate =2020-09-27 | archive-date =2020-10-02 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201002080029/https://www.dailysabah.com/politics/diplomacy/turkey-azerbaijan-military-drills-intimidate-armenia-president-aliyev-says/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>。在9月下旬，亞美尼亞參與俄羅斯在高加索地區的聯合軍演，演習地點包括亞美尼亞境內和[[阿布哈茲|阿布哈茲]]、[[南奧塞梯|南奧塞梯]]兩個[[有限承认国家列表|未受國際普遍承認國家]]，後兩者普遍被國際社會視為[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]的一部份<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1027268.html?__cf_chl_jschl_tk__=924dd755b978e09cfec74649f70d036bb4c8e3e6-1601297188-0-ATaHuBrBb8fCbTK53HzhJ7gX29h5O1mCDyhDtJbxnoOaEj5kIYkBpnCpl7rZIX-VQmvgsaHvKXjBubdcQ0YR_HqEjfegdDoNdi_APgg9ofPW4vbmcDCGQvlI5FqE6aOoKU-6is1bRbaqRi309dPsHgaiYRTjqriTEBq8wqPUxjjWcync5j42_Uwh1eE6IN3EdOdCNzD7xcAZTtxLtiryiqHmzZEug3SH8_U-SwS-xGIEAoGjI-sWPWB93TXrLKuF9x9AhurTOP6kr15j1CziMfNMIvp7QPsOBlzsikIyXxJp |title=Armenia joins Russia, China and others for Caucasus 2020 major international military drills |date=2020-09-10 |access-date=2020-09-28 |website=armenpress.am |publisher=Armenpress（亚美尼亚通讯社） |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002080042/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1027268.html?__cf_chl_jschl_tk__=924dd755b978e09cfec74649f70d036bb4c8e3e6-1601297188-0-ATaHuBrBb8fCbTK53HzhJ7gX29h5O1mCDyhDtJbxnoOaEj5kIYkBpnCpl7rZIX-VQmvgsaHvKXjBubdcQ0YR_HqEjfegdDoNdi_APgg9ofPW4vbmcDCGQvlI5FqE6aOoKU-6is1bRbaqRi309dPsHgaiYRTjqriTEBq8wqPUxjjWcync5j42_Uwh1eE6IN3EdOdCNzD7xcAZTtxLtiryiqHmzZEug3SH8_U-SwS-xGIEAoGjI-sWPWB93TXrLKuF9x9AhurTOP6kr15j1CziMfNMIvp7QPsOBlzsikIyXxJp%2F |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://civil.ge/archives/369450 |title=Russian-led Kavkaz-2020 Drills Start in Abkhazia, Tskhinvali |date=2020-09-21 |access-date=2020-09-27 |website=civil.ge |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002080053/https://civil.ge/archives/369450 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在第75屆[