== 交戰进程 ==
這項交戰的時間軸主要依靠於交戰方的正式聲明。交戰的特點是使用[[大砲|重型火砲]]、[[堑壕战|堑壕战]]、包括[[坦克|坦克]]在內的裝甲戰和[[無人機|無人機]]戰，特別是使用土耳其製造的[[拜拉克塔尔-TB2|拜拉克塔尔-TB2]]無人機和以色列{{le|滯空型彈藥|loitering munition}}[[哈洛普自杀式无人机|哈洛普自杀式无人机]]，以及[[集束炸彈|集束炸彈]]的新報導，在國際上大多數國家禁止使用集束炸彈，但亞美尼亞或阿塞拜疆並未禁止使用集束炸彈<ref>{{Cite web|title=United Nations Treaty Collection|url=https://treaties.un.org/Pages/ViewDetails.aspx?src=TREATY&mtdsg_no=XXVI-6&chapter=26&lang=en|access-date=2020-10-05|website=treaties.un.org|language=EN|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618150323/https://treaties.un.org/Pages/ViewDetails.aspx?src=TREATY&mtdsg_no=XXVI-6&chapter=26&lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及對平民的[[彈道導彈|彈道導彈]]襲擊。

爭奪領土的數量相對有限，但由於在國際邊界上部署和散佈的彈藥種類，衝突已擴大到納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫邊界以外。砲彈和火箭彈落在伊朗[[東亞塞拜然省|東亞塞拜然省]]，儘管沒有造成任何損害<ref>{{Citation|last=Hashemzadeh|first=Mehri|title=اصابت راکت به روستای خلف بیگلو خسارت مالی و جانی نداشت|date=2020-09-27|url=https://www.isna.ir/news/99070604539/|editor-last=Teymouri|editor-first=Robab|publisher=Iranian Students News Agency|language=fa|access-date=2020-09-28|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020123611/https://www.isna.ir/news/99070604539/%D8%A7%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%AA-%D8%B1%D8%A7%DA%A9%D8%AA-%D8%A8%D9%87-%DB%8C%DA%A9%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%A2%D8%B0%D8%B1%D8%A8%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%82%DB%8C|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[伊朗|伊朗]]擊落了幾架無人機<ref>{{Cite web|last=Geopolitics.news|date=2020-09-30|title=Iran shoots down suspected Azerbaijani drone|url=https://geopolitics.news/euroasia/iran-shoots-down-suspected-azerbaijani-drone/|access-date=2020-10-05|website=Geopolitics News|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010123414/https://geopolitics.news/euroasia/iran-shoots-down-suspected-azerbaijani-drone/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title='Мы предупреждали Алиева!': Иран сбил азербайджанский военный самолёт|url=https://avia.pro/news/my-preduprezhdali-alieva-iran-sbil-azerbaydzhanskiy-voennyy-samolyot|access-date=2020-10-05|website=avia.pro|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002115459/https://avia.pro/news/my-preduprezhdali-alieva-iran-sbil-azerbaydzhanskiy-voennyy-samolyot|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]方面指出有兩架無人機在[[卡赫季州|卡赫季州]]墜毀<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://police.ge/en/shinagan-saqmeta-saministros-gantskhadeba/14025 |title=Statement of the Ministry of Internal Affairs |publisher=格鲁吉亚外交部 |access-date=2020-10-07 |date=2020-10-07 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010123414/https://police.ge/en/shinagan-saqmeta-saministros-gantskhadeba/14025 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

