=== 10月1日 ===
凌晨1:00，阿塞拜疆国防部宣布阿塞拜疆军队摧毁向不同方向移动的许多敌方军事纵队<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/unichtozheny-voennye-kolonny-protivnika-video-32472.html |title=Уничтожены военные колонны противника |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195609/https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/unichtozheny-voennye-kolonny-protivnika-video-32472.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据国防部称，在夜间战斗中，阿塞拜疆军队的各单位对驻扎在卡拉巴赫战斗区的亚美尼亚武装部队的阵地进行了炮击<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/v-hode-nochnyh-boev-byli-naneseny-artillerijskie-udary-po-protivniku-video-32474.html |title=В ходе ночных боев были нанесены артиллерийские удары по противнику - видео |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195603/https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/v-hode-nochnyh-boev-byli-naneseny-artillerijskie-udary-po-protivniku-video-32474.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，摧毁了敌军的若干炮兵设施<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://az.sputniknews.ru/video/20201001/425079300/azerbaijan-armenia-karabakh-boi.html |title=Как ВС Азербайджана уничтожают артиллерийские установки противника - видео |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160030/https://az.sputniknews.ru/video/20201001/425079300/azerbaijan-armenia-karabakh-boi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亚美尼亚方面在早上表示，为了改善战斗力，敌人试图对部队和手段进行一些重组，但所有这些企图都被亚美尼亚武装部队及时发现并消灭。据纳卡国防军新闻界报道，他还补充说，在昨晚卡拉巴赫战斗区的整个战线上，局势依然稳定<ref>{{Cite web|language=ru|url= https://m.ru.armeniasputnik.am/karabah/20201001/24692498/VS-Karabakha-presekli-peredvizhenie-protivnika-obstanovka-v-zone-konflikta-minuvshey-nochyu.html |title= ВС Карабаха пресекли передвижение противника: обстановка в зоне конфликта минувшей ночью |website=Sputnik Армения|accessdate=2020-10-01}}</ref>。

當天上午，阿塞拜疆国防部报告说，早晨亚美尼亚武装部队恢复炮击[[泰尔泰尔|泰尔泰尔]]市<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/protivnik-snova-podvergaet-artillerijskomu-obstrelu-gorod-terter-32480.html |title=Противник снова подвергает артиллерийскому обстрелу город Тертер |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108222619/https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/protivnik-snova-podvergaet-artillerijskomu-obstrelu-gorod-terter-32480.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据阿塞拜疆总检察长办公室的消息，由于09:00亚美尼亚武装部队对泰尔泰尔的汽车站炮击，一名阿塞拜疆平民被杀害<ref name="Гасанов">{{Cite web |url=https://az.sputniknews.ru/karabakh/20201001/425078927/azerbaijan-armenia-karabakh-boi.html |title=ВС Армении обстреляли Тертер: погиб еще один мирный житель Азербайджана |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160028/https://az.sputniknews.ru/karabakh/20201001/425078927/azerbaijan-armenia-karabakh-boi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亚美尼亚方面宣布击落了属于阿塞拜疆空军的一架飞机和一架直升机，其碎片落在伊朗境内。阿塞拜疆国防部否认了这一消息，称“阿塞拜疆空军所有飞机都已准备就绪，可以全面使用”。据阿塞拜疆国防部称，阿塞拜疆领土遭到亚美尼亚从[[戈里斯|戈里斯]]地区发射的火箭弹射击，同时从亚美尼亚发射的炮弹击中了[[杰布拉伊尔|杰布拉伊尔]]-[[菲祖利|菲祖利]]地区的前线目标<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/territoriya-azerbajdzhana-podverglas-raketnomu-obstrelu-iz-gorusskogo-rajona-armenii-32491.html |title=Территория Азербайджана подверглась ракетному обстрелу из Горусского района Армении |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195627/https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/territoriya-azerbajdzhana-podverglas-raketnomu-obstrelu-iz-gorusskogo-rajona-armenii-32491.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

下午，亚美尼亚方面报告击落了阿塞拜疆空军的三架Su-25攻击机和两架Mi-24直升机。阿塞拜疆国防部否认了亚美尼亚方面摧毁阿塞拜疆空军的各种飞机的报道，并补充说，阿塞拜疆空军在今天的战斗中没有使用战斗机和直升机。阿塞拜疆国防部宣布，杰布拉伊尔地区的Jojug Marjanli村，菲祖利地区的戈拉季兹以及[[戈兰博伊|戈兰博伊]]，泰尔泰尔和[[阿格达姆|阿格达姆]]地区的前线村庄遭到亚美尼亚武装部队的炮击。

當天亞美尼亞确认有104名士兵、23名平民死于冲突，法国《世界报》两名记者遭阿军炮火击中，伤势严重。阿塞拜疆則承認有一名平民死亡<ref name="#1">{{cite news |title=俄、法、美呼吁纳卡冲突双方停火 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/422218734_267106 |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160101/https://www.sohu.com/a/422218734_267106 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，据伊朗媒体报道，有五枚迫击炮弹落入伊朗境内，并炸伤一名6岁儿童<ref>{{cite news |title=纳卡冲突持续，5枚迫击炮弹落入伊朗境内致一儿童受伤 |url=https://dy.163.com/article/FNTEK3130514R9P4.html |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160358/https://dy.163.com/article/FNTEK3130514R9P4.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月2日 ===
阿塞拜疆国防部宣布，到10月2日上午，阿塞拜疆军队已经控制了马达吉兹（Madagiz）周围的高地，并向杰布拉伊尔-菲祖利方向前进。该报告称，夜间摧毁了5个装甲和汽车设备，3个军事基础设施和亚美尼亚一侧的大量人员<ref>[https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/operativnaya-svodka-ministerstva-oborony-32517.html Оперативная сводка Министерства Обороны] {{Wayback|url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/operativnaya-svodka-ministerstva-oborony-32517.html |date=20201112224122 }}. 2 октября 2020 г.</ref>。當地時間晚上8點30分左右，亞美尼亞政府在[[推特|推特]]表示[[阿爾察赫|阿爾察赫]]首都[[斯捷潘纳克特|斯捷潘纳克特]]被對手的導彈擊中高達三次<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/armgov/status/1312068896288133122?s=19 |title=@armgov A few minutes ago, #Stepanakert, the capital city of Republic of #Artsakh, was hit three times by the adversary’s missiles |accessdate=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160101/https://twitter.com/armgov/status/1312068896288133122?s=19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[亚美尼亚武装力量|亚美尼亚武装力量]]第193特种攻击营的[[军旗|军旗]]被[[阿塞拜疆武装力量|阿塞拜疆武装部队]]第6攻击军团在马尔塔克尔特地区俘获<ref>{{cite web |title=Ermənistanın ələ keçirilmiş döyüş bayraqlarının görüntüləri |url=https://report.az/dagliq-qarabag-munaqishesi/ermenistanin-ele-kecirilmis-doyus-bayraginin-goruntuleri/ |website=Report.az |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002121229/https://report.az/dagliq-qarabag-munaqishesi/ermenistanin-ele-kecirilmis-doyus-bayraginin-goruntuleri/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ağdərədə Ermənistan taborunun döyüş bayrağı və sənədləri ələ keçirilib |url=https://sputnik.az/karabakh/20200930/425076270/agderede-Ermenistan-taborunun-doyus-bayragi-ve-senedleri-ele-kecirilib.html |website=sputnik |accessdate=2020-10-02 |language=az |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002121355/https://sputnik.az/karabakh/20200930/425076270/agderede-Ermenistan-taborunun-doyus-bayragi-ve-senedleri-ele-kecirilib.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亚美尼亚外交部发表声明，称愿意和平解决纳卡冲突，并与[[欧洲安全与合作组织|欧洲安全与合作组织]]明斯克小组开展协作。阿塞拜疆总统的助手则表示，“如果亚美尼亚希望避免局势进一步升级，必须首先结束侵略<ref>{{cite news |title=亚美尼亚称愿意与欧安组织合作 讨论纳卡停火 |url=https://dailynews.sina.com/gb/international/chinapress/2020-10-02/doc-ihaaqscx9794894.shtml |publisher=僑報 |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019071833/https://dailynews.sina.com/gb/international/chinapress/2020-10-02/doc-ihaaqscx9794894.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。

阿爾察赫國防部表示有54名军人陣亡，累计158人死亡<ref>{{cite news |title=亚美尼亚人和亚塞拜然激战 纳卡区已158人丧命 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/contenu/20201002-亚美尼亚人和亚塞拜然激战-纳卡区已158人丧命 |publisher=法广 |accessdate=2020-11-24 |archive-date=2020-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015081353/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/contenu/20201002-%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%9A%E5%A1%9E%E6%8B%9C%E7%84%B6%E6%BF%80%E6%88%98-%E7%BA%B3%E5%8D%A1%E5%8C%BA%E5%B7%B2158%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%A7%E5%91%BD |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月3日 ===
亚美尼亚国防部发言人阿尔斯通·霍夫汉尼斯扬说，在阿塞拜疆将新部队转移到那里之后，10月2-3日晚上发生了激烈的战斗。 军事新闻部长苏珊·斯捷潘尼扬（Shushan Stepanyan）说：“敌人将大量部队集中在这些侧翼上，并发动了进攻。亚美尼亚的小分队阻击了敌人的进攻，给他们造成了沉重的损失”<ref>{{cite news|title=Армения сообщила об ожесточенных боях в Карабахе на двух направлениях|url=https://www.rbc.ru/politics/03/10/2020/5f7809969a79476f1b255fda?utm_source=yxnews&utm_medium=desktop|publisher=РБК|date= 2020-10-03|accessdate=2020-10-03|archive-date=2020-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008021535/https://www.rbc.ru/politics/03/10/2020/5f7809969a79476f1b255fda?utm_source=yxnews&utm_medium=desktop|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並表示阿军已伤亡2745人，仅在2日就阵亡540人；123架无人机、14架直升机、14架固定翼飞机、335辆装甲车辆被摧毁<ref name=“搜狐来源”/>。

阿塞拜疆国防部新闻发言人瓦吉夫·达格里（Vagif Dargahli）说，阿塞拜疆的攻击无人机继续摧毁亚美尼亚武装部队的军事装备。阿塞拜疆国防部称，阿塞拜疆军队“正在对敌人采取报复措施”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/v-nastoyashee-vremya-protivnik-podvergaet-obstrelu-nashi-sela-prinimayutsya-reshitelnye-otvetnye-mery-32579.html |title=В настоящее время противник подвергает обстрелу наши села, принимаются решительные ответные меры |accessdate=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107195728/https://mod.gov.az/ru/news/v-nastoyashee-vremya-protivnik-podvergaet-obstrelu-nashi-sela-prinimayutsya-reshitelnye-otvetnye-mery-32579.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並宣佈阿军控制了[[菲祖利区|菲祖利区]]的一些村庄<ref>{{cite news |title=纳卡地区首府遭炮击 双方已伤亡数千人 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/422673394_162758 |accessdate=2020-10-05 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160148/https://www.sohu.com/a/422673394_162758 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月4日 ===
[[File:InShot_20201020_202248937.webm|thumb]]市使用集束彈藥的影片]]

早晨，[[斯捷潘纳克特|斯捷潘纳克特]]市遭到阿塞拜疆炮击，部分建筑燃起大火<ref name=“搜狐来源”>{{cite web |title=纳卡冲突进入第八天 地区首府遭到炮击 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/422601853_267106 |accessdate=2020-10-05 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160143/https://www.sohu.com/a/422601853_267106 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

阿塞拜疆称亚美尼亚方[[占賈導彈襲擊|炮击该国第二大城市占贾]]，此举将进一步导致冲突事态升级<ref>{{Cite news|title=Azerbaijan says Armenian forces shell second city in major escalation|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-armenia-azerbaijan-idUSKBN26P08I|newspaper=Reuters|date=2020-10-04|accessdate=2020-10-04|language=en|first=Nailia Bagirova, Nvard|last=Hovhannisyan|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161832/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-armenia-azerbaijan-idUSKBN26P08I|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞美尼亞國防部否認這是從其領土來的<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ria.ru/20201004/karabakh-1578171671.html |title=Армения заявила, что не ведет обстрел населенных пунктов Азербайджана |website=ria.ru |publisher=RIA Novosti |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=ru |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008201831/https://ria.ru/20201004/karabakh-1578171671.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而阿爾察赫軍隊負責人指出亞美尼亞部隊已經瞄準並摧毀了[[占賈國際機場|占賈國際機場]]上的軍事基地<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030235.html |title=Ganja military airbase is 'no more' - Artsakh says |website=armenpress.am |publisher=Armenpress |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008201839/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030235.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；阿塞拜疆對此予以否認。隨後，來自俄羅斯媒體的現場報導以及機場主任說，由於病毒大流行，該機場自3月以來一直沒有運轉<ref>{{Cite web|title=Война в Карабахе. Обстрел Степанакерта и удар по Гяндже - Новости на русском языке|url=https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-54317944|access-date=2020-10-04|website=BBC News Русская служба|language=ru|archive-date=2020-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008201843/https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-54317944/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

大約14:00，阿塞拜疆聲稱阿塞拜疆部隊在他的掩體中重傷了上午訪問過陣地的阿爾察赫總統[[阿拉伊克·阿魯秋尼揚|阿魯秋尼揚]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/Presidential-aide:-%22As-a-result-of-our-army's-accurate-strike-Araik-Arutunyan-was-severely-wounded%22-332030 |title=Presidential aide: “As a result of our army’s accurate strike, Araik Arutunyan was severely wounded” |website=APA.az |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |quote=H. Hajiyev said the cluster bombs are launched on the Azerbaijani cities: “Armenia is a terrorist state. Azerbaijan doesn’t leave any of these attacks without response. As of now, it is stated that this fire was inflicted from the occupied territories by order of head of the so-called Nagorno Garabagh Republic Araik Arutunyan. I would like to appeal from here to Araik Arutunyan. Araik Artunyan, you were hiding in bunker, the Azerbaijani army found you even there. As a result of accurate strike of our army, Araik Arutunyan was severely wounded. The same fate awaits other separatists as well”. |archive-date=2020-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012130754/https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/Presidential-aide%3A-%22As-a-result-of-our-army%27s-accurate-strike-Araik-Arutunyan-was-severely-wounded%22-332030 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；被阿爾察赫否認<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030279.html |title=Artsakh denies Azeri reports claiming president is wounded |website=armenpress.am |publisher=Armenpress |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008201902/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030279.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大約一個小時後，阿塞拜疆國防部發佈亞美尼亞火力支援、裝甲和後勤部隊遭到破壞的影片。大約16:00，阿塞拜疆國防部表示，亞美尼亞部隊正用大砲向位於[[阿格賈貝迪區|阿格賈貝迪區]]的Sarıcalı，位於[[阿格達姆區|阿格達姆區]]的Baharlı，Çıraqlı和Üçoğlan和位於[[巴爾達區_(阿塞拜疆)|巴爾達區]]的Şahvəlilər射擊。大約40分鐘後，阿塞拜疆總統阿利耶夫宣布，阿塞拜疆軍隊已控制了[[傑布拉伊爾區|傑布拉伊爾區]]的[[傑布拉伊爾|傑布拉伊爾]]，Karxulu，Şükürbəyli，Yuxarı Maralyan，Çərəkən，Daşgəsən，Horovlu，Mahmudlu和Deccal<ref name="9morevillages">{{Cite web |url=https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/President-Ilham-Aliyev:-Jabrayil-city-and-9-villages-of-the-region-liberated-from-occupation-332056 |title=President Ilham Aliyev: Jabrayil city and 9 villages of the region liberated from occupation |website=APA.az |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |quote=President İlham Aliyev said the city of Jabrayil and 9 villages of the region were liberated from the occupation: Today, Karkhulu, Shukurbayli, Chereken, Dashkasan, Horovlu, Mahmudlu, Jafarabad, Yukhari Maralyan, Decal villages of Jabrayil region have been liberated from occupation. Love to the Azerbaijani army! Karabakh is Azerbaijan!" |archive-date=2020-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012125210/https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/President-Ilham-Aliyev:-Jabrayil-city-and-9-villages-of-the-region-liberated-from-occupation-332056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿爾察赫總統發言人否認傑布拉伊爾被阿塞拜疆控制<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030301.html |title=Artsakh denies Aliyev’s claim on Azeri forces capturing Jabrayil |website=ARMENPRESS |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008201041/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030301.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

阿塞拜疆國防部在大約22:40稱，亞美尼亞軍隊用火箭炮向[[泰爾泰爾|泰爾泰爾]]和[[明蓋恰烏爾|明蓋恰烏爾]]開火<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://apa.az/en/frontline-news/Armenia-fired-on-Azerbaijan's-Mingachevir-and-Tartar-332075 |title=Armenia fired on Azerbaijan's Mingachevir and Tartar |website=APA.az |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |quote=The Mingachevir and Terter cities of Azerbaijan have come under rocket fires from the Armenian armed forces has, there are wounded, the Ministry of Defence told APA. |archive-date=2020-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201012130613/https://apa.az/en/frontline-news/Armenia-fired-on-Azerbaijan%27s-Mingachevir-and-Tartar-332075 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後者擁有大型水庫，亞美尼亞將其視為軍事目標<ref>{{cite news|title=Մի համազարկ` եւ կենտրոնական Ադրբեջանը ծով կդառնա|url=http://hetq.am/arm/news/46664/mi-hamazark-ev-kentronakan-adrbejany-tsov-kdarna.html|work=Hetq Online|date=2010-08-16|language=hy|accessdate=2020-10-05|archive-date=2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517061708/http://hetq.am/arm/news/46664/mi-hamazark-ev-kentronakan-adrbejany-tsov-kdarna.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；亞美尼亞和阿爾察赫都否認了這一點<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030349.html |title=Artsakh and Armenia deny Azerbaijani false information of striking Mingachevir |website=armenpress.am |publisher=Armenpress |date=2020-10-04 |access-date=2020-10-04 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201008213952/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1030349.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月5日 ===
