在夜間，阿塞拜疆國防部指出，其部隊奪取了對其他領土的控制權，衝突繼續以不同的強度繼續。美国国务院表示，新的人道主义停火协议於10月26日上午8时正式生效<ref>{{cite news |title=美国宣布纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫新停火协议 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/5635215.html |accessdate=2020-10-26 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160740/https://www.voachinese.com/a/5635215.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月26日-美國斡旋的停火 ===
早晨，停火再次被打破<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-10-26|title=Nagorno-Karabakh conflict: US-brokered ceasefire frays soon after starting|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-54686284|access-date=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160813/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-54686284|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據阿塞拜疆的說法，亞美尼亞部隊在08:05開始砲擊，而根據亞美尼亞的說法，阿塞拜疆的火砲在08:45開始砲擊亞美尼亞陣地<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-54686682?ns_mchannel=social&ns_source=twitter&ns_campaign=bbc_live&ns_linkname=5f965d1b8baf0c02d0e7a096%26%D0%90%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F%20%D0%B8%20%D0%90%D0%B7%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%B4%D0%B6%D0%B0%D0%BD%20%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%8F%D0%B2%D0%BB%D1%8F%D1%8E%D1%82%20%D0%BE%20%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%83%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B8%20%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%8F%262020-10-26T05%3A22%3A36.412Z&ns_fee=0&pinned_post_locator=urn:asset:a570b389-2c0e-40ab-8b09-5ea8913fceb7&pinned_post_asset_id=5f965d1b8baf0c02d0e7a096&pinned_post_type=share |title=Армения и Азербайджан заявляют о нарушении перемирия |date=2020-10-26 |access-date=2020-10-26 |publisher=BBC Russian Service |language=ru |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124170120/https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-54686682?ns_mchannel=social&ns_source=twitter&ns_campaign=bbc_live&ns_linkname=5f965d1b8baf0c02d0e7a096%26%D0%90%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F+%D0%B8+%D0%90%D0%B7%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%B4%D0%B6%D0%B0%D0%BD+%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%8F%D0%B2%D0%BB%D1%8F%D1%8E%D1%82+%D0%BE+%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%83%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B8+%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%8F%262020-10-26T05%3A22%3A36.412Z&ns_fee=0&pinned_post_locator=urn%3Aasset%3Aa570b389-2c0e-40ab-8b09-5ea8913fceb7&pinned_post_asset_id=5f965d1b8baf0c02d0e7a096&pinned_post_type=share |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 10月27日 ===
