阿塞拜疆指责亚美尼亚对[[巴爾達_(阿塞拜疆)|巴爾達]]发动导弹袭击，造成5人死亡，13人受伤<ref>{{cite news |title=阿塞拜疆：亚美尼亚发动导弹袭击致4人死亡 |url=https://k.sina.com.cn/article_5182171545_134e1a99902000x0as.html?from=news&subch=onews |accessdate=2020-10-28 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113231038/https://k.sina.com.cn/article_5182171545_134e1a99902000x0as.html?from=news&subch=onews |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=土耳其强烈谴责亚美尼亚对阿国平民的“非人道袭击” |url=https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/10/28/tu-er-qi-qiang-lie-qian-ze-ya-mei-ni-ya-dui-a-guo-ping-min-de-fei-ren-dao-xi-ji-1517168 |accessdate=2020-10-28 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120160834/https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/tu-er-qi/2020/10/28/tu-er-qi-qiang-lie-qian-ze-ya-mei-ni-ya-dui-a-guo-ping-min-de-fei-ren-dao-xi-ji-1517168 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===10月30日===
交戰雙方在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日內瓦|日內瓦]]會見了調解員，並同意不會故意將納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫衝突中的平民視為目標。<ref>[https://m.dw.com/en/nagorno-karabakh-armenia-azerbaijan-agree-to-avoid-targeting-civilian-populations-amid-peace-talks/a-55454758 Nagorno-Karabakh: Armenia, Azerbaijan agree to avoid targeting civilian populations amid peace talks] {{Wayback|url=https://m.dw.com/en/nagorno-karabakh-armenia-azerbaijan-agree-to-avoid-targeting-civilian-populations-amid-peace-talks/a-55454758 |date=20201124170056 }} DW， 2020-10-31.</ref>當天，阿塞拜疆国防部表示，阿格德雷、霍贾文德和古巴德利遭到了攻击。亚美尼亚方面则表示，亞美尼亞方挫败了阿塞拜疆人的进攻，並恢复对一些地区的炮击<ref>{{cite news |title=阿塞拜疆与亚美尼亚在日内瓦举行和谈 双方冲突未停 |url=https://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2020-10-30/doc-iiznezxr9030177.shtml |accessdate=2020-11-01 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107201301/https://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2020-10-30/doc-iiznezxr9030177.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

