<ref name="bneIranArmeniaarmsshipment">{{Cite news |url=https://www.intellinews.com/iran-denies-allowing-passage-of-weapons-into-armenia-after-video-emerges-on-social-media-192945/ |title=Iran denies allowing passage of weapons into Armenia after video emerges on social media |website=intellinews.com |publisher=IntelliNews |date=2020-09-29 |access-date=2020-09-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209154219/https://www.intellinews.com/iran-denies-allowing-passage-of-weapons-into-armenia-after-video-emerges-on-social-media-192945/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月29日[[伊朗外交部|伊朗外交部]]長否認該指控<ref name="Irandeniesarmstrade1">{{Cite web |url=https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/NewsView/612094 |title=Spokesman Denies Claim That Arms Transferred via Iran to Armenia |website=mfa.gov.ir |publisher=Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Islamic Republic of Iran |date=2020-09-29 |access-date=2020-09-29 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930142643/https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/NewsView/612094 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隔日，阿塞拜疆國營電視台發佈了一些軍備正在經伊朗運送的鏡頭<ref name="AzerbaijanclaimsIRARMarmstrade1">{{Cite news |url=https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/Video-footages-spread-regarding-weapons-and-military-equipment-transport-from-Iran-to-Armenia-colorredNEW-FACTScolor-colorredVIDEOcolor-331624 |title=Video footages spread regarding weapons and military equipment transport from Iran to Armenia - NEW FACTS - VIDEO |website=APA.az |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930142803/https://apa.az/en/nagorno_garabagh/Video-footages-spread-regarding-weapons-and-military-equipment-transport-from-Iran-to-Armenia-colorredNEW-FACTScolor-colorredVIDEOcolor-331624 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AzerbaijanclaimsIRARMarmstrade2">{{Cite news |url=https://www.azernews.az/karabakh/169670.html |title=Military supplies for Armenia being shipped through Iran [PHOTO/VIDEO] |website=azernews.az |publisher=AzerNews |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930142908/https://www.azernews.az/karabakh/169670.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/politics/3307948.html |title=Military supplies for Armenia being shipped through Iran (PHOTO/VIDEO) |website=trend.az |publisher= |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930143038/https://en.trend.az/azerbaijan/politics/3307948.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[国民议会_(阿塞拜疆)|阿塞拜疆國民議會]]議員{{le|沙比尔·鲁斯塔姆汉利|Sabir Rustamkhanli}}質疑伊朗參與運送武器至亞美尼亞的行動<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://report.az/milli-meclis/mm-kubada-sefirlik-tesis-olunmasi-layihesini-qebul-etdi/ |title=Deputat: "İran müxtəlif ölkələrdən gələn silah-sursatı Ermənistana daşımaqla məşğuldur" |website=Report.az |publisher=Report Information Agency |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=az |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930143135/https://report.az/milli-meclis/mm-kubada-sefirlik-tesis-olunmasi-layihesini-qebul-etdi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於國民議會提議在[[以色列|以色列]]開設[[大使館|大使館]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://apa.az/en/foreign-news/Opening-Azerbaijani-Embassy-to-Israel-suggested-in-Azerbaijani-Parliament-331631 |title=Opening Azerbaijani Embassy to Israel suggested in Azerbaijani Parliament |website=APA.az |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930121234/https://apa.az/en/foreign-news/Opening-Azerbaijani-Embassy-to-Israel-suggested-in-Azerbaijani-Parliament-331631 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊朗總統府辦公室首長在9月30日致電阿塞拜疆總理，否認相關指控並指這些言論意論意在破壞兩國關係<ref name="Irandeniesarmstrade2">{{Cite news |url=https://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/2841669/%D8%B4%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%B1-%DA%A9%D9%85%DA%A9-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A7-%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA |title=شایعات مبنی بر کمک ایران به ارمنستان کاملا بی اساس است |website=iribnews.ir |publisher=伊朗伊斯兰共和国广播电视台 |date=2020-09-30 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=fa |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930143337/https://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/2841669/%D8%B4%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%A8%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%B1-%DA%A9%D9%85%DA%A9-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D9%86-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A7-%D8%A8%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伊朗國營電視台指画面中的卡車事實上是在運送亞美尼亞早前向俄羅斯[[卡馬汽車廠|卡馬汽車廠]]購買的汽車<ref name="Irandeniesarmstrade4">{{Cite news |url=https://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/2841827/%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%88%D9%86%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AE%D8%A7%DA%A9-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86 |title=انتقال کامیونهای روسی از خاک ایران! |website=iribnews.ir |publisher=[[伊朗伊斯兰共和国广播电视台|伊朗伊斯兰共和国广播电视台]] |date=2020-09-29 |access-date=2020-09-30 |language=fa |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930143710/https://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/2841827/%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84-%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%88%D9%86%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B3%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B2-%D8%AE%D8%A7%DA%A9-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在9月28日，俄羅斯媒體報道該國有[[私人軍事服務公司|私人軍事服務公司]]已經準備好參與納卡地區的戰事以對抗阿塞拜疆<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ura.news/news/1052451658 |title=Российские наемники готовы отправиться в Карабах |first=Maxim |last=Anfalov |website=ura.news |date=2020-09-28 |access-date=2020-10-02 |language=ru |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002202945/https://ura.news/news/1052451658 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月1日，[[自由歐洲電台／自由電台|自由歐洲電台]]宣稱引用來自[[瓦格納集團|瓦格納集團]]的消息，該私人軍事服務公司已經參與在納卡地區的戰事<ref name="WagnerGroupRFE" >{{Cite web |url=https://www.svoboda.org/a/30868597.html |title="Россия ослабела из-за авантюр Путина". Поможет ли Москва Еревану? |website=svoboda.org |publisher=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty |date=2020-10-01 |access-date=2020-10-02 |language=ru |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120183637/https://www.svoboda.org/a/30868597.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

阿塞拜疆總統最初表示[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]]不允許武器通過其領土運輸，並感謝格魯吉亞作為夥伴和朋友<ref>{{cite news |title=Azerbaijani president Aliyev: Georgia has prevented transit for arms supply for Armenia |url=https://agenda.ge/en/news/2020/2914 |work=Agenda.ge |date=September 2020 |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161355/https://agenda.ge/en/news/2020/2914 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 但是，在隨後的採訪中，他聲稱亞美尼亞濫用其[[伊尔-76|伊尔-76]]貨機中的一架進行民用飛行，秘密運輸戰鬥人員和[[9M133短號反坦克导弹|9M133短號反坦克导弹]] 從俄羅斯通過格魯吉亞領空進入亞美尼亞<ref>{{Cite web|title=Алиев: Иран и Грузия закрыли воздушное пространство и наземные дороги для доставки оружия в Армению|url=https://report.az/ru/nagorno-karabakhskiy-konflikt/aliev-iran-i-gruziya-zakryli-vozdushnoe-prostranstvo-i-nazemnye-dorogi-dlya-dostavki-oruzhiya-v-armeniyu/|access-date=2020-10-28|website=Информационное Агентство Репорт|language=ru|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161357/https://report.az/ru/nagorno-karabakhskiy-konflikt/aliev-iran-i-gruziya-zakryli-vozdushnoe-prostranstvo-i-nazemnye-dorogi-dlya-dostavki-oruzhiya-v-armeniyu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 格魯吉亞對此作出回應，稱其領空對所有軍隊和軍事貨運航班均不開放，但對民用和人道主義航班開放。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-17|title=Karabakh: Georgia Says Not Responsible for Civilian Flights|url=https://civil.ge/archives/375897|access-date=2020-10-28|website=Civil.ge|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120161423/https://civil.ge/archives/375897|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====塞爾維亞====
